sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Bridge as ERP–UNS Bridge
    participant API as BC API Layer
    participant Inbox as Integration Inbox
    participant Exec as Operation Execution

    note over Bridge,Exec: Scenario: Duplicate Message (Network Retry)

    Bridge->>API: POST /executionEvents<br/>{ messageId: "uuid-abc-123",<br/>orderNo: "PO-4711", operationNo: "10",<br/>qtyProduced: 500, sourceTimestamp: "T1" }

    API->>Inbox: Check messageId exists?
    Inbox-->>API: Not found

    API->>Inbox: INSERT record<br/>Status = "Received"
    API->>Exec: UPSERT execution KPIs
    API->>Inbox: UPDATE Status = "Processed"

    API-->>Bridge: 200 OK<br/>{ processed: true, isNew: true }

    note over Bridge,Exec: Network timeout – Bridge retries same message

    Bridge->>API: POST /executionEvents<br/>{ messageId: "uuid-abc-123",<br/>orderNo: "PO-4711", operationNo: "10",<br/>qtyProduced: 500, sourceTimestamp: "T1" }

    API->>Inbox: Check messageId exists?
    Inbox-->>API: Found (Status = "Processed")

    note over API: Skip processing –<br/>already handled

    API-->>Bridge: 200 OK<br/>{ processed: true, isNew: false,<br/>note: "Duplicate messageId" }

    note over Bridge,Exec: Result: No duplicate records created

